# Create a custom role

1) As developer try to run a new app (i.e. tomcat).
   Check that everything is ok then delete it

2) Switch to system:admin and create a new 'view' role which can get pods

3) Assign the new role and delete the 'admin' role to developer user

4) As developer try to run a new app

5) Switch back to system:admin

6) Recover initial roles

7) Delete the new created role
